---
// 热门推荐产品组件 - 按设计稿实现
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 animate-fade-up">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- 标题 -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6 text-gray-800 animate-fade-up animate-delay-100">
      HOT RECOMMENDED PRODUCTS
    </h2>
    
    <!-- 描述文字 -->
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-fade-up animate-delay-200">
      From the procurement of raw materials to the assembly of products, every step of the process
      strictly follows the international quality management system standards.
    </p>
    
    <!-- 产品展示区域 -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- 产品1 -->
      <div class="product-card bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 card-hover-animate animate-fade-up animate-delay-300">
        <div class="product-image-container overflow-hidden">
          <img 
            src="/images/skid1-400.webp" 
            alt="滑移装载机" 
            width="400"
            height="240"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">滑移装载机 YN-S850</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">紧凑设计，动力强劲，适用于狭窄空间作业</p>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">¥180,000</span>
            <a href="/products/skid-steer-loader-s850" class="btn-primary text-sm">查看详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 产品2 -->
      <div class="product-card bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 card-hover-animate animate-fade-up animate-delay-400">
        <div class="product-image-container overflow-hidden">
          <img 
            src="/images/backhoe-400.webp" 
            alt="挖掘装载机" 
            width="400"
            height="240"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">挖掘装载机 YN-B120</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">一机双能，兼具挖掘与装载功能</p>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">¥350,000</span>
            <a href="/products/backhoe-loader-b120" class="btn-primary text-sm">查看详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 产品3 -->
      <div class="product-card bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 card-hover-animate animate-fade-up animate-delay-500">
        <div class="product-image-container overflow-hidden">
          <img 
            src="/images/telescopic-400.webp" 
            alt="伸缩臂叉车" 
            width="400"
            height="240"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">伸缩臂叉装车 YN-T3500</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">超长臂展，高空作业的理想选择</p>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">¥420,000</span>
            <a href="/products/telescopic-handler-t3500" class="btn-primary text-sm">查看详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 查看更多按钮 -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a href="/products" class="inline-flex items-center border-2 border-red-600 text-red-600 px-8 py-3 hover:bg-red-600 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 animate-fade-up animate-delay-600">
        查看更多产品
        <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* 产品卡片固定尺寸 - 防止CLS */
  .product-card {
    height: 480px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .product-image-container {
    width: 100%;
    height: 240px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: #f3f4f6;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .product-card .p-6 {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  /* 移动端优化 */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .product-card {
      height: auto;
      min-height: 400px;
    }

    .product-image-container {
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style> 